                        Telesales means sale over the telephone, the short western name of the telemarketing job. This
                        is often considered a job for students and new graduates applying for jobs because it is quite
                        easy to apply for, large and small companies often hire a lot. Job description: go through the
                        training program, grasp the product, read the script (the script), receive the phone number
                        list, settle down on the chair and start calling. Call from start to finish. If you are lucky,
                        you will have the opportunity to meet people who have given you the opportunity to present and
                        find a way to close a successful sale. You will receive a commission on the product you sell,
                        the more you sell, the higher the month-end bonus. If you are unlucky, you will just sit in that
                        chair all day, every day, just call. <br><br>

                        The work seemed to be just sitting in a cold room all day, but in fact, it is extremely hard and
                        suffered a lot of resentment. Being cursed, hung up in the middle, scolded for being scolded is
                        a lot, politely answering or agreeing to buy a new part, very little.<br><br>

                        <h5>So how can customers not refuse to give up their time to listen to your phone, listen to
