                        Listen to your customers, pay attention to their information to divide them into market
                        segments. Segmentation by geographic location (regions, regions, demographics (such as age,
                        gender, occupation, income), psychographic segments such as personality, buying habits, and
                        preferences of customers ... You have to know the strengths and weaknesses of customers to know
                        what you need advice to provide them.Customers will be very welcome if you provide them with
                        useful information they do not know or what there is. value to them Don't sell like a robot that
                        can only read the original script. <br><br>
